data.description: Delightful single story offers many recent updates and upgrades.  Wood or tile floors welcome you in all living areas and bedrooms except the primary bedroom which features neutral carpet. The kitchen showcases beautiful white cabinetry, granite countertops, a sparkling sink, a faucet and a dishwasher all replaced in 2022.  Enjoy the open floor plan offering a spacious family room with a wood-burning fireplace open to the kitchen and breakfast room. The primary bath cabinets were freshly painted and plumbing fixtures in the dual sinks were replaced in May 2023.  The secondary bath was remodeled in 2022.  A private neighborhood park/playground is within walking distance and the elementary school is conveniently located just outside the subdivision. This home is move-in ready and sure to please. Some photos have been virtually staged.
